  "title": "Village (Blue) Route Shuttle Bus - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_828672\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_6949515_828672\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481828\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_6949515_481828\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Village (Blue) Route Shuttle Bus</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6374634\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6954657\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6954657\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"An outdoor shuttle bus terminal. In the foreground, about a dozen people are sitting under an open air shade pavilion. On their right, a line of people about to board a green and white bus.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/P1370495.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"P1370495 August 1, 2021\"/>\n<figcaption>Park Visitors about to board the Village (Blue) Route bus at the Visitor Center Shuttle Bus Terminal. This is the view seen walking east from the Visitor Center Plaza. The eastbound and westbound Kaibab (Orange) Route shuttle also stop here. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS/M. Quinn 8/1/2021</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6949520\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6949520\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/P1370329.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"a white and green bus is unloading passengers by a rustic open bus stop with a shake roof. in the background, a four story hotel.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/P1370329.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"P1370329\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>The Village (Blue) Route shuttle at the train depot stop. El Tovar Hotel is in the background. </figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2>Village <span style=\"color:#0033ff;\">(Blue)</span> Route </h2>\n<p><strong>This route provides a transportation loop between the Visitor Center Plaza, lodges, restaurants, campgrounds, the Backcountry Information Center, and Market Plaza (general store and post office). </strong></p>\n<h3>Spring Schedule</h3>\n<p><strong>March 1, through May 22, 2026</strong><br/>\n50 minutes round trip (without getting off the bus)</p>\n<p><strong>First bus at 7:00 am — the last bus is at 9:00 pm.<br/>\n► Be at a bus stop no later than 8:45 pm.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Every 15 minutes: 7:00 am to 10:00 am</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Every 9 minutes: 10:00am to 6:00 pm</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Every 15 minutes: 6:00 pm to 9:00 pm</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Village service ends at 9:00 pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6949521\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6949521\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Village</span><span style=\"color:#0000cc;\"> (Blue) </span><span style=\"color:null;\">Route - Need to Know</span></h2>\n<p><strong>Canyon views are a short walk from the following bus stops: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/places/000/train-depot-village-blue-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6648551,train-depot-village-blue-route.htm,31100|\">Train Depot</a> - </strong>follow the paved footpath up the hill behind the bus stop.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/places/000/bright-angel-lodge-village-blue-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6648533,bright-angel-lodge-village-blue-route.htm,31100|\">Bright Angel Lodge</a> - </strong>the canyon is just behind the bus stop, beyond the buildings.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"/places/000/hermits-rest-route-transfer-village-blue-route.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644939,hermits-rest-route-transfer-village-blue-route.htm,31100|\">Hermit Road Transfer Station</a> - </strong>as you exit the bus, walk to your left to the overlook.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>The Canyon Rim Trail and greenway trails</strong> can be accessed via this route – however, be aware of ice and snow during winter months (and sometimes during spring) along these trails.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please refer to the loop diagram below, along with the <strong><a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/news/upload/sr-pocket-map.pdf\">South Rim Pocket Map and Services Guide</a></strong> (1.1 MB PDF file) for more information about this route.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6949545\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6949545\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Blue Route Shuttle loop map showing all stops\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/blue-loop-diagram.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"blue-loop-diagram.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>Map showing the Village Loop (blue) shuttle bus stops </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6949525\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6949525\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>What to See - Points of Interest</h2>\n<p>(also shown on the maps above, and below)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/grand-canyon-visitor-center.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2230772,grand-canyon-visitor-center.htm,11006|\">Grand Canyon Visitor Center</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/market-plaza-grca-south-rim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6749361,market-plaza-grca-south-rim.htm,11006|\">Market Plaza</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/shrine-of-the-ages.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2231877,shrine-of-the-ages.htm,11006|\">Shrine of the Ages</a> and <a href=\"/places/000/park-headquarters-3.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644992,park-headquarters-3.htm,31100|\">Park Headquarters</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/train-depot.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644968,train-depot.htm,31100|\">Train Depot</a><strong> </strong>(This is the stop for<strong> </strong><a href=\"/places/000/el-tovar-hotel.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644959,el-tovar-hotel.htm,31100|\">El Tovar Hotel</a>,<strong> </strong><a href=\"/places/000/hopi-house.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644961,hopi-house.htm,31100|\">Hopi House</a><b> and </b><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/verkamps.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2162913,verkamps.htm,11006|\">Verkamp’s Visitor Center</a>)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/bright-angel-lodge.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644947,bright-angel-lodge.htm,31100|\">Bright Angel Lodge</a><strong> </strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"/places/000/maswik-lodge.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644980,maswik-lodge.htm,31100|\">Maswik Lodge</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/lookout-studio.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644949,lookout-studio.htm,31100|\">Lookout Studio</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/art-exhibits.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2143883,art-exhibits.htm,11006|\">Kolb Studio</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/bright-angel-trail.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644998,bright-angel-trail.htm,31100|\">Bright Angel Trail</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/places/000/backcountry-information-center.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6644982,backcountry-information-center.htm,31100|\">Backcountry Information Center</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/mather-campground-south-rim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6774226,mather-campground-south-rim.htm,11006|\">Mather Campground</a><strong> and </strong><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/trailer-village-rv-park-south-rim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=6772884,trailer-village-rv-park-south-rim.htm,11006|\">Trailer Village</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6374631\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<a id=\"map\"></a><a id=\"CP_JUMP_6374631\"></a><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6374631\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>South Rim Shuttle Bus Route Map</h2>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_854153\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_854153\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Map showing South Rim Grand Canyon Village and Vicinity showing three shuttle bus routes that are in service during the spring. The 4 routes are indicated by blue, orange purple and red lines.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/South-Rim-Pocket-Map-3000-wide-copy-spring-2026.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"\"/>\n<figcaption>This spring, 3 shuttle bus routes are in service from March 1, through May 22, 2026. Kaibab Rim (Orange) Route, shown on the right, transports visitors to S. Kaibab Trailhead, outstanding scenic views at Yaki Point, and Yavapai Geology Museum. Village (Blue) Route, center, connects the Visitor Center with lodges, campgrounds, Backcountry Information Center, and Market Plaza (general store and post office). Hermits Rest (Red) Route, on the left) follows a scenic road for exceptional canyon views. </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2666053\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2666053\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<em><strong>When walking or cycling at the Grand Canyon, make sure to take your time and carry food and water with you. The South Rim of Grand Canyon averages 7,000 feet / 2,134 meters above sea level. Visitors with respiratory or heart problems may experience difficulties. Exercising at this elevation can be strenuous.</strong></em>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7060997\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7060997\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Shuttle Bus Route List</span></h2>\n<h4><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1914943,/grca/planyourvisit/shuttle-buses.htm,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Shuttle Bus Home Page</a><br/>\n</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/village-blue-route.htm\">Village (Blue) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/kaibab-orange-route.htm\">Kaibab Rim (Orange) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hiker-express-shuttle.htm\">Hikers' Express Shuttle</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/hermit-red-route.htm\">Hermit Road (Red) Route</a> <strong><span style=\"color:#339900;\">In Operation</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"> </span>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/tusayan-route-purple.htm\">Tusayan Park &amp; Ride (Purple) Route</a><strong><font color=\"#660099\"> </font><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Not in Service </span><span style=\"color:#339900;\">- Summer 2026 Only</span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 28, 2026</p>\n</div>